{"tid":2373503,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工做錯野 成日調節唔到","createTime":"2021-01-20T13:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T03:19:23.000Z","uid":196666,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8875318529c57feddd64528a036f547fb2e88645","tid":2373503,"uid":196666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩轉行又未過試用期<br />\n但返工會唔熟手所以都要人幫手check野<br />\n然後未係好了解公司文化同同事 今年又WFH<br />\n自己係內部溝通做得唔夠好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係啲新人必犯既錯 又mark低咗提自己冇下次<br />\n但情緒調節唔到 覺得自己好蠢唔夠人醒<br />\n就黎3個月又仲大壓力 因為腦細會期望你pickup好晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知大家點調節同埋通常做幾耐先開始上軌道"},{"pid":"76d1df88599fecf3c95c5857526d0ebcc479b348","tid":2373503,"uid":279640,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"3個月其實好短時間，唔使咁大壓力。同一樣錯唔好重複犯就得啦。"},{"pid":"c1ffc97e01b03ac33569e897248ec5a3064b0197","tid":2373503,"uid":101307,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"比人屌都事小 做極唔識先事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14357a0d3bd74cc6a78537a01a1b9ca62014bd8a","tid":2373503,"uid":242275,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"翻新工做sale 依家2個月都未搵到新客/未正式落單<br />\n自卑到日日唔想翻工<br />\n最2個星期情緒好低落覺得自己係垃圾<br />\n終於調節翻 今日突然又覺得好絕望"},{"pid":"71dff3a285efa1db7f55bfdfec6bb553988e4996","tid":2373503,"uid":196666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"76d1df88599fecf3c95c5857526d0ebcc479b348","tid":2373503,"uid":279640,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"3個月其實好短時間，唔使咁大壓力。同一樣錯唔好重複犯就得啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:50:59.000Z","msg":"feel到腦細有啲微言 搵咗經理提我<br />\n但啲野真係冇經驗 handle得唔好我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d888476e51559ecd66f6ca78ea088f6b76228d6","tid":2373503,"uid":196666,"like"